quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  57,12,"√Ďalnde yi'oytaa gom…óim…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gom…óim…ďe rew…ďe …ďen, hara annoora ma…ď…ďe yaara yeeso ma…ď…ďe e √Īaamo ma…ď…ďe (…ďe wi'anee): \"Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mun, ko on duumotoo…ďe nder ton\". Ko …óum woni malal mawngal ngal"
  57,13,"√Ďalnde naafiqii…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e naafiqii…ďe rew…ďe …ďen wi'anoyta gom…óim…ďe …ďen: \"Habbee men, men jalbinora annoora mon on\". ∆Āe wi'anee : \"Yiltoree …ďaawo mon, …óa…ď…ďoyon annoora\". Heedo wa…óee hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mun, …ďaawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mun"
  57,14,"Hi…ďe nodda …ďe : \"E men wondaano e mon?\" ∆Āe wi'a : \"Ko non woniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitani…óon [gom…óim…ďe …ďen bone], sikkiti…óon, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e mo∆ī∆īere Allah nden"
  57,15,"Hannde on, on ja…ďantaake soktor…óum wanaa e …ďen yeddu…ďe. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hanndu…óon. Nge bonii ruttorde"
  57,16,"E yontaani gom…óim…ďe …ďen nde …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen dee∆īirta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara …ďe wa'aali wa …ďen okkanoo…ďe Defte …ďen ko adii, dumunna on juutani …ďen, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yoori, ko …óuu…óunoo e ma…ď…ďe kon ko faasiqii…ďe"
  57,17,"Anndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay leydi ndin …ďaawo ndi yoorii. Gom…óii Men …ďannginiranii on Aayeeje …óen, fii no haqqiliron"
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotoo…ďe (jawle mun …ďen) ka wor…ďe e ka rew…ďe …ďe √Īawli Allah √Īamaande labaande, …ďe sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani …ďe njo…ďdi mawndi"
